{
  "stem": "13623.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At the end of the day, somebody says, we're going to the town called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That town had a railroad-- railroad track, a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "The reason we walked there is because where we were at our ghetto, there was no railroad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As we approached, we saw a long line of railroad cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we all got closer to the place, there were soldiers surrounding the-- the railroad-- all the railroad cars and us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they rushed us to board those cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They said, throw down whatever you have.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "The only thing you can take is your food that you have with you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "You're not going to need anything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A lot of chaos ensued to that point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Because men, husbands and wives, children in the walk got lost.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "A lot of-- a lot of chaos, again, like the scene that we had before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Husbands were calling their wives names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Children were looking for their parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "But they have rushed us so much to walk in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Luckily, my family, my immediate family, my mother and father and siblings, did get together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And we were together in the same car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "But other people, children wound up in cars with total strangers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And, now, we're all in the cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "We're all loaded up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 100 to 120 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We're all-- we're in the car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody is thirsty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody is tired from the walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very quiet in the car, except for both children and-- and adults, you would hear, subdued cries from people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was-- we were tired.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
